csv

Class UnquotedCsvLineParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • csv.UnquotedCsvLineParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICsvLineParser

    public class UnquotedCsvLineParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICsvLineParser
    A class used to parse a String given in a CSV format without quotes, specified at construction. Parsing without quotes can be faster, but you can't escape the delimiters then.
